{"type": "article", "id": 61751, "title": "NAP 发售女性权益主题联名 T 恤，洽洽推出瓜子脸面膜 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-05T04:58:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 137, "name": "女性"}, {"id": 295, "name": "跨界"}, {"id": 57061, "name": "洽洽"}, {"id": 1329, "name": "天猫"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190305124235hcN8KqfZwVxyQ2ml.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p line=\"AOv6\"><a href=\"http:// https://m.weibo.cn/status/4344274294404492?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>洽洽联合护肤品牌春纪推出瓜子脸面膜，</b></a>不过品牌提示消费者，“瓜子脸”和实际功效无关。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124301y6x9ZJTjQ5a0wzuc.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555404\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"QCa1\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4345546262596386?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3 月 3 日 天猫金妆奖发布新产品天猫精灵 QUEEN，天猫之前拍了支广告片来介绍新产品的功能。</a></b>传统镜子背后的美人穿越到了现代生活中，她和化妆镜的跨时代对话来展现了天猫精灵 QUEEN 能提供化妆光源、检测皮肤状态等功能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e08441jzf18\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"9beS\"><a href=\"https://www.net-a-porter.com/us/en/porter/article-4730e355031b1d84/incredible-women/incredible-women/international-women-day-2019-t-shirts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>国际妇女节之际，Net-A-Porter 和 6 位女性设计师合作推出独家 T 恤。</b></a>设计师分别是 Victoria Beckham、Isabel Marant、Ellery、Rosie Assoulin、Alexa Chung 和 Perfect Moment。每款 T 恤的设计都用简短的标语来支持女性权益。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124345jkKhisYDA5PNbEQ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703512\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124358xpsSzjBmX5CgLRdD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666842\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p line=\"WOFy\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTQwMzU4MQ==&amp;mid=2652270836&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=28260de9393e51f0a7af5eef84458aae&amp;chksm=bcded9a68ba950b0858baeb11d61b9a1e6edb3185688fe8c72a07b55da1bda9da3d7b87e4bb9&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0305VKvbgIIQWwtRHydFdi7C&amp;key=e26fe09897582c58ebdc86b60cc512cc6c9e44dda8ad482b1e5609a5702bf7dde7d6bb7fced86b9c5a505bf61675803f83f64e9cbb45d9ca2df9255d33dc3ae4dbdb941fa570463fe86e0c5f09926d26&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=Gv4HhK3N1i3Bo9dZ8zLb9M%2Bj8bhvIQxqCqBwE1GYAwRSvkwDyPeVoy89VLfgGSsi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>玉兰油的妇女节广告围绕着“年龄”主题来讨论。</b></a>品牌找来明星和普通女性来展示每位女性值得关注的是人生经历年龄而非生理年龄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f0844t5sq2n\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z0844mrhdiz\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"dGwX\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/rKo-vh1GNM8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>耐克的韩国妇女节广告 <em>Choose Phenomenal </em>着眼在女性的自主选择上。</b></a>片中出演的包括韩国女性运动员，以及名人、歌手和 K-Pop 明星，紧随耐克奥斯卡 <em>Dream Crazier </em>上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r0845mn21t4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"PsKf\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4345164757336676?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>KATE 和 %Arabica 咖啡合作开了间隐形 % 咖啡馆。</b></a>参加者在门口领取 % 咖啡兑换券，五种咖啡口味分别对应 KATE 新品粉底液的五个色号。兑换券投入点单处，之后会有相应的咖啡推出。活动时间为 3 月 1 日--3 月 3 日和 3月 8 日-- 3 月 10 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124605dsvbW1zuFnpl9OaP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124605lJGKgNpWcVkdoZzj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124605kQU9AhYdCf30gioZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124605O2kI1XCFoDclLaST.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124606XyrVkuUPOTpNZ7wh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030512460521TPYz0hlUC8GKf4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305124605aSPEQRxkuK5TgDAc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"6A1f\"><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/album/5779742\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Vimeo 上线了转变经营战略后的首个品牌广告，表示专注于为创作者服务。</b></a>14 支很短的广告片讲述了一些古怪无助的场景，Vimeo 虽然帮不上忙，不过如果涉及到视频时候倒是可以的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t0845y4bsur\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\">同时， Viemo 还发布了一系列户外广告来宣传自己的服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305125225UP9yrwIxXDnK2pm4.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.587140\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051252252mtZdA4LK6Y39IRg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754991\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051252269l6V8s5eKNFGZfu1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.315625\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305125226RF4oA8O9WNIdGJc2.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.638281\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030512522657Nwk2EQSPZ3Y01B.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566406\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305125226lPLdXkysMUZ3EeQw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691781\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190305125227pWqeL8DEiJUgAIZx.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.433594\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903051252275aWZ8jVC6pFkSlRQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.578906\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"ZjBe\"><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/agencyspy/international-paralympic-committee-selects-adameveddb-as-its-first-creative-agency/154108\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>国际伤残奥林匹克委员会（IPC，简称“国际残奥委会”）将 adam＆eveDDB 作为它成立 30 周年之际第一个合作的创意机构。</b></a>adam＆eveDDB 将无偿和 IPC 合作，来提高 IPC 的品牌的认知度和价值。</p><p line=\"db5F\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/starbucks-and-ariana-grande-tease-collaboration-2019-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>星巴克将和歌手 Ariana Grande 合作推出新饮品。</b></a>星巴克最开始在 Twitter 上征集云的名字（cloud name），之后又陆续发布了一系列与云有关的图片和推文，而 Grande 本人也很喜欢云，她也发布了包含云和咖啡 emoji 的推文暗示即将开始的合作。</p><p line=\"Q4sj\">题图来自：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/woVoM7dKGTk?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Les Anderson</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/women-power?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}